{"analytics_identifier":"OT1326","base_path":"/government/organisations/uk-national-screening-committee","content_id":"afb55c90-1986-4ac8-bd0b-3944b836493e","description":"The UK National Screening Committee (UK NSC) advises ministers and the NHS in the 4 UK countries about all aspects of screening and supports implementation of screening programmes. UK NSC is part of the Department of Health and Social Care , the Welsh Government , The Scottish Government , and the Department of Health (Northern Ireland) .","details":{"acronym":"UK NSC","alternative_format_contact_email":"uknsc@dhsc.gov.uk","body":"<div class=\"govspeak\"><p>The UK National Screening Committee (UK NSC) advises ministers and the NHS in the 4 UK countries about all aspects of screening and supports implementation of screening programmes.</p>\n\n<p><abbr title=\"UK National Screening Committee\">UK NSC</abbr> is part of the <a class=\"brand__color\" href=\"/government/organisations/department-of-health-and-social-care\">Department of Health and Social Care</a>, the <a class=\"brand__color\" href=\"/government/organisations/welsh-government\">Welsh Government</a>, <a class=\"brand__color\" href=\"/government/organisations/the-scottish-government\">The Scottish Government</a>, and the <a class=\"brand__color\" href=\"/government/organisations/department-of-health-northern-ireland\">Department of Health (Northern Ireland)</a>.</p>\n</div>","brand":"department-of-health","default_news_image":{"high_resolution_url":"https://assets.publishing.service.gov.uk/media/6993053175466636847f6b92/s960_UK_NSC_logo_on_open_laptop.png","url":"https://assets.publishing.service.gov.uk/media/69930531492ea446ea7f4464/s300_UK_NSC_logo_on_open_laptop.png"},"foi_exempt":false,"logo":{"crest":"custom","formatted_title":"UK National Screening Committee","image":{"alt_text":"UK National Screening Committee","url":"https://assets.publishing.service.gov.uk/media/60d5a9dad3bf7f7c389ab26d/UK_NSC_logo.png"}},"ordered_corporate_inform